021/**
022 * Represents an <c>atomLink</c> construct in the RFC4287 specification.
023 *
024 * <h5 class='figure'>Schema</h5>
025 * <p class='bschema'>
026 *    atomLink =
027 *       element atom:link {
028 *          atomCommonAttributes,
029 *          attribute href { atomUri },
030 *          attribute rel { atomNCName | atomUri }?,
031 *          attribute type { atomMediaType }?,
032 *          attribute hreflang { atomLanguageTag }?,
033 *          attribute title { text }?,
034 *          attribute length { text }?,
035 *          undefinedContent
036 *       }
037 * </p>
038 *
039 * <ul class='seealso'>
040 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="../../../../../overview-summary.html#juneau-dto.jd.Atom">Overview &gt; juneau-dto &gt; Atom</a>
041 *    <li class='jp'><a class="doclink" href="package-summary.html#TOC">package-summary.html</a>
042 * </ul>
043 */
044@Bean(typeName="link")
045@FluentSetters
046public class Link extends Common {
047
048   private String href;
049   private String rel;
050   private String type;
051   private String hreflang;
052   private String title;
053   private Integer length;
054
055
056   /**
057    * Normal constructor.
058    *
059    * @param rel The rel of the link.
060    * @param type The type of the link.
061    * @param href The URI of the link.
062    */
063   public Link(String rel, String type, String href) {
064      setRel(rel).setType(type).setHref(href);
065   }
066
067   /** Bean constructor. */
068   public Link() {}
